1
00:00:34,840 --> 00:00:38,970
My day-to-day life at that
time was a complete mess.

2
00:00:39,450 --> 00:00:42,210
I can't say it was the fault of youth.

3
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:48,020
I was a student at a music college,
but I had a part-time job delivering copy.

4
00:00:48,860 --> 00:00:53,390
A certain girl referred me to it, and I
was extremely well-suited to the job.

5
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:16,420
Some punk like you had a wreck.

6
00:01:16,490 --> 00:01:19,980
Flirting with his girl and not watching
the road. Lucky he's not dead.

7
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:22,460
This poor old man's gonna be though.

8
00:01:22,590 --> 00:01:25,530
Listen! Get it there in an hour!
You're fired if you don't!

9
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,100
The accident outline and the film.

10
00:01:37,270 --> 00:01:38,300
Thanks.

11
00:01:42,940 --> 00:01:48,210
Hello, hello. Yeah. Yeah. What? When?
This morning? Did you check around?

12
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,010
Please excuse me.

13
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:56,160
Just cigarettes? Cheeky.

14
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:00,720
Thank you.

15
00:02:02,030 --> 00:02:03,090
Thanks.

16
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,360
- Thanks.
- Hey, come here!

17
00:02:13,510 --> 00:02:15,870
You said you'd fix it before the last case!

18
00:02:16,110 --> 00:02:17,600
I'm gonna be late!

19
00:02:17,850 --> 00:02:18,900
Whatever.

20
00:02:24,590 --> 00:02:25,750
Hey, Hashimoto.

21
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,150
Yeah?

22
00:02:31,330 --> 00:02:33,120
Take responsibility for my sister.

23
00:02:38,430 --> 00:02:40,700
- What do you mean?
- What are you gonna do?

24
00:02:41,700 --> 00:02:43,830
I didn't say you could break up with her.

25
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:49,010
It's between Fuyumi-san and I.

26
00:02:49,180 --> 00:02:50,240
Shut up!

27
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:52,410
You put the moves on her.

28
00:02:53,350 --> 00:02:54,820
She was a virgin.

29
00:02:55,420 --> 00:03:00,010
She wouldn't have ridden off with someone
unless they put the moves on her.

30
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:02,720
I'll give you two or three days, got it?

31
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:04,960
Think hard!

32
00:03:38,830 --> 00:03:40,620
Ko Hashimoto

